{"id":14646,"date":"2023-05-18T13:44:56","date_gmt":"2023-05-18T13:44:56","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:10011\/?p=14646"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:23:19","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:23:19","slug":"wien-international-scholarship-program","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wien-international-scholarship-program\/","title":{"rendered":"Wien International Scholarship Program (WISP) to Study in USA 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-gmghn-79elbk h-full dark:bg-gray-800\">\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-gmghn-1n7m0yu\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center text-sm dark:bg-gray-800\">\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\">\n<div class=\"flex p-4 gap-4 text-base md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl md:py-6 lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\">\n<p>Brandeis University in the United States of America is excited to announce the opening of applications for the Wien International Scholarship Program (WISP) for eligible international students seeking to pursue a degree program at the university in the upcoming academic session.<\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_65 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Contents on This Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wien-international-scholarship-program\/#Wien_International_Scholarship_Program_Summary\" title=\"Wien International Scholarship Program Summary\">Wien International Scholarship Program Summary<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wien-international-scholarship-program\/#WIEN_International_Scholarship_Program_WISP_Details\" title=\"WIEN International Scholarship Program (WISP) | Details\">WIEN International Scholarship Program (WISP) | Details<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wien-international-scholarship-program\/#Eligibility_Criteria\" title=\"Eligibility Criteria\">Eligibility Criteria<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wien-international-scholarship-program\/#Application_Procedures\" title=\"Application Procedures\">Application Procedures<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>Established in 1958, the WISP is a pioneering program that has been instrumental in attracting students from diverse backgrounds worldwide to the vibrant campus of Brandeis University. With a focus on fostering active global citizenship, this program creates a dynamic environment that engages the entire community in the pursuit of knowledge and cross-cultural exchange.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"wien-international-scholarship-program-summary\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wien_International_Scholarship_Program_Summary\"><\/span>Wien International Scholarship Program Summary<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between lg:block\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full border-t md:border-t-0 dark:border-white\/20 md:border-transparent md:dark:border-transparent md:bg-vert-light-gradient bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 md:!bg-transparent dark:md:bg-vert-dark-gradient pt-2\">\n<form class=\"stretch mx-2 flex flex-row gap-3 last:mb-2 md:mx-4 md:last:mb-6 lg:mx-auto lg:max-w-2xl xl:max-w-3xl\">\n<div class=\"relative flex h-full flex-1 items-stretch md:flex-col\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"h-full flex ml-1 md:w-full md:m-auto md:mb-2 gap-0 md:gap-2 justify-center\">\n<p><strong>Scholarship Sponsor(s):\u00a0\u00a0<\/strong>Brandeis University, USA<\/p>\n<p><strong>Host Institution(s)<\/strong>: \u00a0Brandeis University, USA<\/p>\n<p><strong>Scholarship\u00a0Worth:\u00a0<\/strong>Full-fee Scholarship<\/p>\n<p><strong>Number of Awards<\/strong>:\u00a0 Several<\/p>\n<p><strong>Study Level<\/strong>:\u00a0 Undergraduate<\/p>\n<p><strong>Nationality<\/strong>: International students<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"wien-international-scholarship-program-wisp-details\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WIEN_International_Scholarship_Program_WISP_Details\"><\/span><strong>WIEN International Scholarship Program (WISP) | Details<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Wien International Scholarship Program has brought over 894 scholars from 115 countries to Brandeis, and its graduates continue to be committed to Brandeis University and to improving the world.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"eligibility-criteria\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligibility_Criteria\"><\/span><span id=\"Eligibility_Criteria\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>Eligibility Criteria<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Eligible applicants for this scholarship are expected to meet the following eligibility criteria;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Applicants must be international student.<\/li>\n<li>All undergraduate courses and subjects in science, the arts, politics, business, and the humanities offered by the university are eligible.<\/li>\n<li>Applicants must meet all the following\/given criteria:<\/li>\n<li>The applicants must be active in extracurricular activities and other non-academic activities.<\/li>\n<li>The applicants must be enrolled and accepted into the university.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"application-procedures\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Procedures\"><\/span><span id=\"Application_Procedures\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>Application Procedures<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>How-to-Apply:\u00a0\u00a0<\/strong>Interested and eligible applicants for the Wien International Scholarship Program (WISP) to study at Brandeis University in the United States are required to apply using the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/apply.gsas.brandeis.edu\/account\/login?r=https%3a%2f%2fapply.gsas.brandeis.edu%2fapply%2f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">university application portal<\/a>.<\/li>\n<li>The applicants can also apply through the\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/apply.commonapp.org\/login?ma=41\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Common Application<\/a><\/strong>.<\/li>\n<li>Accepted students who fit the eligibility of the award will be considered.<\/li>\n<li>The applicants must submit the following documents:<\/li>\n<li>Official Transcripts<\/li>\n<li>Letters of Recommendation<\/li>\n<li>School profile<\/li>\n<li>Resume<\/li>\n<li>Work experience<\/li>\n<li>Financial documentation<\/li>\n<li>Statement of purpose<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.brandeis.edu\/isso\/programs\/wien\/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Visit the Official Website for Further Details<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/form>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Brandeis University in the United States of America is excited to announce the opening of applications for the&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":14648,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14646"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14646"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14646\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/14648"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14646"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":